- FORBIDDEN examples: "medium shot" (0 posts), "bust shot" (incorrect term)
- SAFE examples: "cowboy shot" (729K posts), "upper body" (1.01M posts), "full_body" (892K posts)

CRITICAL TAG FORMAT RULES:
- ALWAYS use underscores, NEVER spaces: "thumbs_up" ✓, "thumbs up" ✗
- NEVER combine multiple adjectives into one tag: "short green hair" ✗
- SEPARATE attributes into individual tags: "short_hair, green_hair" ✓
- Copy tag format EXACTLY from Allowed Keywords list (with underscores)

